gui

Class GUIPage

  • java.lang.Object
    • gui.GUIPage
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    About, CreateProject, EditAccount, Home, Login, NewProject, RegisterAccount

    public abstract class GUIPage
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Robert on 4/12/17. A GUIPage defines the build method that will be called by the GUI when a page is changed. Basically that method will define what components go on the page and the functions that buttons call also should be defined here as GUIPages act as the model and bridge between the control and view.
